EVTDESC36907;In 1847, writer William Makepeace Thackeray published 'Vanity Fair', a work criticizing the unspirited and artificial world of the so-called better circles.;En 1847, l'?crivain William Makepeace Thackeray a publi? ""La Foire aux vanit?s""", un roman qui critiquait le monde terne et hypocrite de la pr?tendue bonne soci?t?.

