anti_trust_laws_desc;This legislation stopped concentration of power on the market. Sometimes an actor became too big and competition diminished on the market which meant that prices was raised unproportionally.;Cette l?gislation mettait un terme aux fortes concentrations du march?. Il arrivait en effet qu'un acteur du march? devienne trop "gros" et emp?che la concurrence d'op?rer, ce qui provoquait une hausse disproportionn?e des prix.

